oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lucy G. Drane in a Buick Automobile
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lucy G. Drane in a Buick automobile. Drane is sitting in the drivers seat and has two children next to her. The photograph was taken at West Avenue in Clarksville, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Automobiles; Vehicles; Roads; Women
